<hr>


<p>
This course is an introduction to Natural Language Processing (with mainly deep-learning approach). The  lab
sessions use the <a href="https://pytorch.org/">pytorch (python module)</a>.  
</p>

<div id="outline-container-org4ed00a3" class="outline-2">
